keyFacts: The document is an email forwarding a meeting invitation for a case preparation call.
The case referenced is USA v. Ghislaine Maxwell, docket number 20 CR 330 (AJN).
The meeting was scheduled for November 24, 2021, from 2:00 PM to 2:30 PM Eastern Time.
The meeting was to be conducted via Microsoft Teams, indicating remote coordination.
The email addresses appear to be redacted or generic placeholders (e.g., 'testimony'), suggesting this is an internal or procedural communication.
